      &lt;h2 class=&quot;my-0 mb-[16px] text-ellipsis text-[18px] font-medium text-emphasis&quot;&gt;
        延伸阅读
      &lt;/h2&gt;
      
          &lt;a referrer=&quot;null&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20250604-6564721&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;title&quot; id=&quot;mobile-recommend-articles&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              下午察：李在明入主青瓦台 中韩关系将回暖？
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;relative min-w-[120px] w-[120px]&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img alt=&quot;下午察：李在明入主青瓦台 中韩关系将回暖？&quot; title=&quot;下午察：李在明入主青瓦台 中韩关系将回暖？&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/739aca5032170a8b57b2a45f6cfeac2c7dd32599f22a9c515ac1f7e43ca578c8&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
                      &lt;div class=&quot;absolute left-0 top-0 flex aspect-[3/2] h-full w-full items-center justify-center&quot;&gt;
                        
                        
                        
